race.comment: DUNSTALL THE GUN (1) returns after five months in the paddock. Closed the last campaign with a fourth over 1500m at Muswellbrook. Rates on top and is a great chance to break through. SIPPING SHAMUS (2) wasn't far off maiden success before a break of five months, finishing the campaign with a minor placing over 1400m at Tamworth. Good chance to break through. RUBINSKY (7) showed good speed and fought on for second over 1000m at Kempsey last time. Sure to be competitive. IMOTOSAN (11) is a Showtime filly on debut for the Cavanough stable. Showed improvement in most recent trial and can make her presence felt.
